2. Patch SearchController
2.1 Add interaction tracking

Add helper:

import time

def _mark_interaction(self, action: str):
    self.store.update(
        last_interaction_ts=time.time(),
        last_action=action,
    )
2.2 Patch all entry points

Example:

def set_query_text(self, text):
    self._mark_interaction("query")
def set_preset(self, preset_id):
    self._mark_interaction("preset")
def apply_filter(self, filter_key, value):
    self._mark_interaction("filter")
Why

👉 This enables UX-level behaviors like:

debounce
smarter refresh
animation triggers
user intent detection
3. Patch TopSearchBar
